हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: They killed his family, stole his legacy, and shattered his name… But now, hidden beneath a new identity, he returns not just to destroy them — but to make them beg for mercy, as he to become their worst nightmare but who is he ?
